{"tid":571106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登成功爭取巴士延長罷工","createTime":"2018-02-24T11:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T11:15:48.000Z","uid":124410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f9493a5ae0b21553f5dc0a575ad238bccb24e41d","tid":571106,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:00:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382380-20180224.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382380-20180224.htm&d=uttWRRIPV6qOO%2Fem%2FmZFa6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=7de94b19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382380-20180224.htm&h=df3554a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382380-20180224.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n九巴車長組織「月薪車長大聯盟」晚上8時發起工業行動，並由原定維持半小時，延長至4小時，至午夜12時結束。九巴發出內部通告，指如有任何違反工作指引的行為，公司必定作出嚴厲紀律處分。<br />\n<br />\n九巴人力資源部發出內部通告，表示知悉員工對近日推出的優化薪酬方案有不同意見及疑慮，但現在衝動行事作出工業行動，對所有持分者會有不良影響。<br />\n<br />\n九巴又提醒車長，必需遵守公司既定指引及交通規則，以乘客服務為先。"},{"pid":"b49a78ecfe4e5b5a24a43d814b522101df2dff2e","tid":571106,"uid":124410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c45dc17bf00edcf5d7a93abd6b01204b558657","tid":571106,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:03:03.000Z","msg":"笑死 仲火上加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159a82e09590995c41a02d695dd8cef8aa28fc86","tid":571106,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:15:48.000Z","msg":"資方完全唔放你在眼內<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}